<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Hello from AlloyDB</title>
<link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 16 16'%3E%3Ctext y='14' font-size='14'%3E%E2%9C%A8%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #f7f8fb;
    --surface: #ffffff;
    --text: #1f2328;
    --muted: #57606a;
    --border: #e4e7eb;
    --accent: #1a73e8;
    --accent-2: #34a853;
    --danger: #d93025;
    --danger-soft: #fce8e6;
    --code-bg: #f3f4f6;
    --shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(16,24,40,.04), 0 8px 24px rgba(16,24,40,.06);
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    :root {
      --bg: #0d1117;
      --surface: #161b22;
      --text: #e6edf3;
      --muted: #8b949e;
      --border: #30363d;
      --accent: #4c8eff;
      --accent-2: #56d364;
      --danger: #ff6b6b;
      --danger-soft: #3a1d1d;
      --code-bg: #0d1117;
      --shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.2), 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
    }
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Inter, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.55;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 48px 24px 64px;
  }
  .hero {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .badge {
    width: 56px; height: 56px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    display: grid; place-items: center;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .badge.error {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d93025, #f29900);
    border-color: transparent;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .badge img { width: 100%; height: 100%; display: block; }
  .badge.error svg { width: 28px; height: 28px; }
  h1 {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .subtitle {
    color: var(--muted);
    margin: 0 0 32px;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  .card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .card + .card { margin-top: 20px; }
  .card-header {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  dl.kv {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 8px 20px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: max-content 1fr;
    gap: 0;
  }
  dl.kv > div { display: contents; }
  dl.kv dt, dl.kv dd {
    padding: 12px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin: 0;
  }
  dl.kv > div:last-child dt,
  dl.kv > div:last-child dd { border-bottom: none; }
  dl.kv dt {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 14px;
    padding-right: 24px;
  }
  dl.kv dd {
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, "SF Mono", Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    word-break: break-all;
  }
  pre.query {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    background: var(--bg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, "SF Mono", Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    overflow-x: auto;
    white-space: pre;
  }
  pre.query .kw { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
  dl.kv dt.sql {
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, "SF Mono", Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  pre.diagram {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 20px 16px;
    background: var(--bg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, "SF Mono", Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    overflow-x: auto;
    text-align: center;
    white-space: pre;
  }
  pre.diagram code {
    display: inline-block;
    text-align: left;
    font-family: inherit;
  }
  ol.steps {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 8px 20px 16px 44px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  ol.steps li {
    padding: 6px 0;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  ol.steps li strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }
  ol.steps code, dl.kv code {
    background: var(--code-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 1px 6px;
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, "SF Mono", Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: 12.5px;
  }
  .next-steps {
    margin-top: 24px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .next-steps a {
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .next-steps a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .error-box {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: var(--danger-soft);
    color: var(--danger);
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, "SF Mono", Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    word-break: break-all;
  }
  footer {
    margin-top: 40px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  footer a {
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  footer a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  footer code {
    background: var(--code-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 1px 6px;
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, "SF Mono", Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <% if (ok) { %>
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="badge" aria-hidden="true">
      <img src="/alloydb.svg" alt="">
    </div>
    <h1>Hello from AlloyDB!</h1>
  </div>
  <p class="subtitle">
    Your Cloud Run service is connected securely to AlloyDB through the Auth
    Proxy.
  </p>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">Live query response from your AlloyDB instance</div>
    <pre class="query">SELECT version(), now(), current_database(), current_user;</pre>
    <dl class="kv">
      <div><dt class="sql">version()</dt><dd><%= version %></dd></div>
      <div><dt class="sql">now()</dt><dd><%= server_time %></dd></div>
      <div><dt class="sql">current_database()</dt><dd><%= database %></dd></div>
      <div><dt class="sql">current_user</dt><dd><%= user %></dd></div>
    </dl>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">How does this app connect to AlloyDB?</div>
    <pre class="diagram" aria-label="Request flow diagram"><code>
                  ┌─────────── Cloud Run service ───────────┐
                  │                                         │
 ┌─────────┐      │  ┌─────┐         ┌──────────────────┐   │      ┌─────────┐
 │ Browser │─────▶│  │ App │────────▶│   Auth Proxy     │───┼─────▶│ AlloyDB │
 └─────────┘      │  └─────┘         │ ──────────────── │   │      └─────────┘
                  │                  │  • mTLS tunnel   │   │
    HTTPS         │  loopback        │  • IAM authn/z   │   │          mTLS
                  │  (no TLS)        │  • cert rotation │   │
                  │                  └──────────────────┘   │
                  └─────────────────────────────────────────┘
</code></pre>
    <ol class="steps">
      <li>Your browser sent a request to this <strong>Cloud Run</strong> service.</li>
      <li>
          The app opened a plain <strong>localhost connection</strong> to the
          <strong>Auth Proxy</strong> sidecar on
          <code><%= host %>:<%= port %></code> &mdash; no TLS config or database
          password in app code.
      </li>
      <li>
          The Auth Proxy called the <strong>AlloyDB API</strong> as its
          <strong>IAM principal (IAM authz)</strong>  to fetch the instance's
          <strong>connection info</strong> and an
          <strong>ephemeral client certificate</strong>, then opened an
          <strong>mTLS</strong> tunnel to the target instance.
      </li>
      <li>
          To log in, the Proxy fetched the IAM principal's
          <strong>OAuth2 access token</strong> and forwarded it to AlloyDB as
          the password &mdash; a <strong>passwordless handshake (IAM authn)</strong>
          from the app's perspective.
      </li>
      <li>
          The Proxy ensures all future connections have a valid connection by
          <strong>auto-rotating the ephemeral certificate every ~12 hours</strong>
          and <strong>using a fresh OAuth2 token</strong> once the current one expires
          (every ~1 hour), all with no app restart required.
      </li>
      <li>
          The app sent the query through the tunnel and received the values
          shown above from the AlloyDB instance.
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <% } else { %>
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="badge error" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h1>Couldn&rsquo;t reach AlloyDB</h1>
  </div>
  <p class="subtitle">
    The app started, but the query to AlloyDB failed. Check the Auth Proxy
    sidecar logs and confirm the values below match your instance.
  </p>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">Error</div>
    <div class="error-box"><%= error %></div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">Configuration</div>
    <dl class="kv">
      <div><dt>Proxy endpoint</dt><dd><%= host %>:<%= port %></dd></div>
    </dl>
  </div>
  <% } %>

  <p class="next-steps">
    Also try <a href="/api/status">/api/status</a> for the same data as JSON.
  </p>

  <footer>
    Served from <code>examples/run</code> &middot;
    <a href="https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/alloydb-auth-proxy/tree/main/examples/run">source</a> &middot;
    <a href="https://cloud.google.com/alloydb/docs/auth-proxy/overview">Auth Proxy docs</a>
  </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>
